## Note

This link should generate the tridiv object of the astro pi base that is used to generate the actual model.

The following adjustments have been made:
* Adjusted border-radius on the `left-box` and the `buttons-box`
* `buttons-box` border-radius adjustments requires to change the rt and lt translation and width resizing
* Removed shaders
* Adjusted textures for the outstanding corners
* Adjusted the textures to avoid stretching

http://tridiv.com/app/index.html?
